item.title: Things I've learned as an intern
item.description: Over the past few months, I’ve had the great opportunity to intern at Intuit doing full-stack development on the Electronic Filing Engine (EFE) team. Between coffee chats, zoom standups, and tedious fights with IntelliJ, here’s a list of tips for success. Learn your tools Learn how to effectively use your editor.
